  title: 'Let it Shine '
  entry: For all the dead- For all the dread Count it. Each soul is burdened by being
    shackled to the confines of this room.   Understand the pain soon to come. give
    us YOUR LIGHT and shine it amongst these nearby walls. We shall reveal what our
    opressors hid from your eyes.
